<sect1 id="SQRT">
  <title>SQRT</title>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">SQRT<indexterm>
      <primary>SQRT</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>SQRT function</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis><emphasis>n</emphasis><emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <para><informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <colspec colwidth="78.45pt" />

        <colspec colwidth="274.35pt" />

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry>n</entry>

            <entry>O número real que será avaliado.</entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry>Return:</entry>

            <entry>SQRT retorna um valor real único.</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable></para>

  <para>A função  <emphasis role="bold">SQRT </emphasis> retorna a raiz quadrada do parâmetro.</para>

  <para>Exemplo:</para>

  <programlisting>MyRoot := SQRT(16.0);</programlisting>

  <para>Ver também: <link linkend="POWER">POWER</link>, <link linkend="EXP">EXP</link>, <link linkend="LN">LN</link>, <link linkend="LOG">LOG</link></para>
</sect1>
